    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Act as an expert Instagram creator. Take the news article provided from the previous GNews node and rewrite it into a snappy, engaging carousel script using the strict JSON output schema provided. Ensure the first slide always uses templateId HOOK_A and the last uses CTA_FINAL.\n\nArticle Title: {{ $('Find First Unposted').item.json.title }}\n\nDescription: {{ $('Find First Unposted').item.json.description }}\n\nContent: {{ $('Find First Unposted').item.json.content }}\n\nImage URL: {{ $('Find First Unposted').item.json.image }}",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are an expert Instagram content creator. You must extract the news, write an Instagram carousel JSON, write an engaging Instagram post caption, and generate 4-5 relevant hashtags.\n\nCRITICAL ARCHITECTURE INSTRUCTIONS: You must output a JSON object strictly matching the connected output parser schema. It must have 3 root keys:\n\ninstagramCaption -> A highly engaging Instagram post caption including emojis.\ninstagramHashtags -> A string of 5 relevant hashtags separated by spaces (e.g. \"#news #tech\").\nremotionManifest -> A JSON object containing the slide data.\nThe remotionManifest object MUST contain these 3 Exact Keys:\n\nformat: MUST be exactly the string \"mp4\".\nglobalBranding: An object with \"accentColor\" (e.g. \"#ef4444\"), \"handle\" (e.g. \"@breaking_news\"), and an \"effects\" array.\ncarousel: An array of slide objects.\nCRITICAL SLIDE RULES (carousel array): Every slide object must have a templateId and a data object.\n\nThe FIRST slide's templateId MUST be exactly \"HOOK_A\".\nThe MIDDLE slides' templateIds MUST be exactly \"CONTENT_LISTICLE\", \"CONTENT_GENERIC\", or \"CONTENT_VIDEO\".\nThe LAST slide's templateId MUST be exactly \"CTA_FINAL\". NEVER invent template names like \"carousel_slide_1\". Use ONLY the ALL-CAPS names listed above."
        }
      },
      "id": "fb62ed1c-16a9-41d6-95c1-0930cdffa1f3",
      "name": "AI Agent - Instagram Creator",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        1300,
        304
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "bb8c5736-718e-443f-98f5-176c6b14d941",
      "name": "Google Gemini Chat Model",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatGoogleGemini",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1300,
        528
      ],
      "credentials": {
        "googlePalmApi": {
          "id": "Eyc8HfzICtgOgRox",
          "name": "Google Gemini(PaLM) Api account"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "schemaType": "manual",
        "inputSchema": "{\n  \"type\": \"object\",\n  \"properties\": {\n    \"remotionManifest\": {\n      \"type\": \"object\",\n      \"properties\": {\n        \"format\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n        \"globalBranding\": {\n          \"type\": \"object\",\n          \"properties\": {\n            \"accentColor\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n            \"handle\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n            \"effects\": {\n              \"type\": \"array\",\n              \"items\": { \"type\": \"string\" }\n            }\n          }\n        },\n        \"carousel\": {\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"items\": {\n            \"type\": \"object\",\n            \"properties\": {\n              \"templateId\": {\n                \"type\": \"string\",\n                \"enum\": [\"HOOK_A\", \"CONTENT_LISTICLE\", \"CONTENT_GENERIC\", \"CONTENT_VIDEO\", \"CTA_FINAL\"]\n              },\n              \"data\": {\n                \"type\": \"object\"\n              }\n            }\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"instagramCaption\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n    \"instagramHashtags\": { \"type\": \"string\" }\n  }\n}\n"
      },
